img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲記得執佢返屋企一落場就咬我,而家想佢咬佢都冇力咬"},{"pid":"c654ac3d85176334f2ce685aa2b58e437d744dd9","tid":87082,"uid":55309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T15:42:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有地方<br />\n肯帶佢周圍玩嘅話<br />\n金毛會幾開心<br />\n又識湊細路<br />\n地方唔大就養史納沙<br />\n比較聰明嘅狗<br />\nBtw幾個月養起最好<br />\n仲要花時間心機去教<br />\n你諗清楚先好養<br />\n又要幫手執屎<br />\n冇得去旅行<br />\n慘過生仔</blockquote><br />\nagger<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n養左西施<br />\n18年無去過旅行<br />\n由幾個月開始養，<br />\n養到18歲就開心行唔到，睇唔到，<br />\n大小便失禁，<br />\n最後去左<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唉</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實唔怕煩係可以帶埋狗仔去旅行<br />\n個別航空公司仲可以帶埋狗仔上cabin</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />知道<br />\n謝謝巴打"},{"pid":"c23bbfecbb00ea94dadd206e04cb33d4e4f07a8a","tid":87082,"uid":55309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T15:43:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有地方<br />\n肯帶佢周圍玩嘅話<br />\n金毛會幾開心<br />\n又識湊細路<br />\n地方唔大就養史納沙<br />\n比較聰明嘅狗<br />\nBtw幾個月養起最好<br />\n仲要花時間心機去教<br />\n你諗清楚先好養<br />\n又要幫手執屎<br />\n冇得去旅行<br />\n慘過生仔</blockquote><br />\nagger<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n養左西施<br />\n18年無去過旅行<br />\n由幾個月開始養，<br />\n養到18歲就開始行唔到，睇唔到，<br />\n大小便失禁，<br />\n最後去左<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唉</blockquote></blockquote><br />\n我有隻7歲poodle都淋巴癌,就夠鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲記得執佢返屋企一落場就咬我,而家想佢咬佢都冇力咬</blockquote><br />\n陪多d佢<br />\n唔好令自己有遺憾"},{"pid":"1256fc0543ed7a047baffd0eaad194cef8871bb3","tid":87082,"uid":71190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T16:14:28.000Z","msg":"最緊要合眼緣 咩品種都唔係大問題"},{"pid":"feb3ca76b06d9afcf9f45fd7074a69976b00acc1","tid":87082,"uid":73730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T16:24:55.000Z","msg":"史納莎 貴婦，因為太聰明，唔識教會有反效果，會好頑皮<br />\n西施都算係比較靜同乖既品種，400尺應該ok<br />\n<br />\n芝娃娃都適合細屋，但睇你彩數同識唔識教<br />\n唔識教會成日都想醒巴佢（我宜家有時都醒巴佢）<br />\n通常都有小聰明，但有啲芝娃娃好神經質<br />\n我果隻就好聰明，教到佢好乖好定"},{"pid":"67899eb7267c9264d536ecfafda67eb46f898f0d","tid":87082,"uid":14990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T19:47:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最緊要合眼緣 咩品種都唔係大問題</blockquote><br />\nAgger<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bcb5db0f112c0b15b7abf47dc4b6186e49006cb","tid":87082,"uid":70062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T20:08:40.000Z","msg":"領養<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實待領養的狗都好靚<br />\n又有性 又有受過訓練"},{"pid":"51a54b37f48222a6df5125fbc5504bf3999daaf8","tid":87082,"uid":70062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T20:11:14.000Z","msg":"買狗仔其實好冇陰公<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果可以請領養<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好心有好報"},{"pid":"d6f45d25c3fea59bc7a45a46428daf455f72cd9b","tid":87082,"uid":17799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T20:17:28.000Z","msg":"拉布拉多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/22/041725_8e4b909cd36bc8dbcf4b768573db8fed.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F22%2F041725_8e4b909cd36bc8dbcf4b768573db8fed.jpg&h=672707ef&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5330947b95003834e7c38856a2383b4b6df374f8","tid":87082,"uid":38351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T09:15:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https:/