class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n塊面要經常做清潔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ded3c0cb3153e3b8e7b1638b47c8e45e8be11b31","tid":87082,"uid":73880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T15:38:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>八哥易唔易養<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔易<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好鬼嘈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n塊面要經常做清潔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好為食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 細個係街度跟住我屋企人尾 最尾跟埋我屋企人返屋企 一養養咗幾年 可惜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80dafe311c518bf97bbbdc5682fcef9e01c15b25","tid":87082,"uid":57962,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T15:43:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c98bcda121792c2800569b3a7119a1049d2d82bf","tid":87082,"uid":43156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T15:51:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔易<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好鬼嘈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n塊面要經常做清潔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好為食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 細個係街度跟住我屋企人尾 最尾跟埋我屋企人返屋企 一養養咗幾年 可惜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁本來嘅主人呢"},{"pid":"5fca48cf5a54fd2240535e0ead9492bb98eef8eb","tid":87082,"uid":25676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T20:30:46.000Z","msg":"細狗好臭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n都係大型狗好"},{"pid":"fbe7c177b9c69beec58053a6568b5858d2b7b4cf","tid":87082,"uid":45055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T20:41:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好鍾意poodle<br />\n要買到樓先會養<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b84237ce825e27b0eb011eb9178f341db7c85a46","tid":87082,"uid":77384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T20:53:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmcCbu7SJpmmPRPfWdQFuQbkcV7eS9m4VCtqAZEDmW734w?filename=Fh8g0d3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFh8g0d3.jpg&h=b1c1c4e3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4c97fcad341207766087c7908343a9d01d0a706d","tid":87082,"uid":25463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T03:12:37.000Z","msg":"簡岩自己既狗唔係簡品種，係簡性格<br />\n金毛都有文靜既，鬥犬種都有斯文既<br />\n你個人係好活潑既簡文靜既點都唔會夾"},{"pid":"5346ab277c773c82770f2fcd4a8de7fe8b5b460d","tid":87082,"uid":11774,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T03:46:07.000Z","msg":"我自己鍾意哥基 但養緊貴婦<br />\n建議樓主上網搵多啲資料先決定<br />\n其實貴婦無上面講到咁難養<br />\n貴婦好聰明 你肯用心教 5分鐘學識sit<br />\n我嗰隻係咁 而且唔多甩毛 無臭味 呢樣真<br />\n我屋企人好怕狗味 但宜家個個都攬住隻狗嚟錫<br />\n而且都幾安靜 好少會嘈 不過就比較痴身 我嗰隻成日扭抱 同埋好鍾意跳 兩隻腳行 好似人咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係就係要日日梳吓毛 抹眼屎 耳屎就1-2日1次<br />\n但你養得就預咗要打理佢 愛佢嘅話 真係日日做都唔會厭啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而且貴婦可以剪唔同造型 好可愛㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n附上我隻衰仔<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qma6v4KZLyNqA6F8F25oDYp4DcnyxbXHjXjozAatDZdEPx?filename=C20o3oG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC20o3oG.jpg&h=fb00d6d6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7beecb6de23ec0068f5390bc76821e011a3eada6","tid":87082,"uid":32585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T12:32:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我自己鍾意哥基 但養緊貴婦<br />\n建議樓主上網搵多啲資料先決定<br />\n其實貴婦無上面講到咁難養<br />\n貴婦好聰明 你肯用心教 5分鐘學識sit<br />\n我嗰隻係咁 而且唔多甩毛 無臭味 呢樣真<br />\n我屋企人好怕狗味 但宜家個個都攬住隻狗嚟錫<br />\n而且都幾安靜 好少會嘈 不過就比較痴身 我嗰隻成日扭抱 同埋好鍾意跳 兩隻腳行 好似人咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係就係要日日梳吓毛 抹眼屎 耳屎就1-2日1次<br />\n但你養得就預咗要打理佢 愛佢嘅話 真係日日做都唔會厭啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而且貴婦可以剪唔同造型 好可愛㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n附上我隻衰仔<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qma6v4KZLyNqA6F8F25oDYp4DcnyxbXHjXjozAatDZdEPx?filename=C20o3oG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC20o3oG.jpg&h=fb00d6d6&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n終於都有人講哥基... 其實佢都好叻又易打理 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有圖有論討<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/23/203154_790d80a2ae63a422f119f19b3d10b383.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F23%2F203154_790d80a2ae63a422f119f19b3d10b383.jpg&h=d6a786cb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e26812219b2410c56d2757dee3f5afbf5196abd5","tid":87082,"uid":57300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T15:40:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如題 請大家給點意見</blockquote><br />\n新手養唐狗，最聽話，易教"},{"pid":"f779b663aef71270f9b58896ed4d3d06ef122c30","tid":87082,"uid":67551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T04:58:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://vignette2.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/2/2d/It-dog.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20160705155901\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvignette2.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2F2%2F2d%2FIt-dog.jpg%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20160705155901&h=d30d15fc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4d4d69cd2fb8f24917cb5c91d69670b9e4fa7d10","tid":87082,"uid":5705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T14:50:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://vignette2.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/2/2d/It-dog.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20160705155901\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvignette2.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2F2%2F2d%2FIt-dog.jpg%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20160705155901&h=d30d15fc&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 出現鳥"},{"pid":"83baf9330547b3ea2c9db7865479237b21037519","tid":87082,"uid":65098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T13:24:35.000Z","msg":"咪聽上面話養貴婦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我自己都有養大狗 次次見d on9主人連隻小狗都教唔掂 比隻狗仔烚 隻狗拉住主人行 真係唔知係人放狗定狗放人 基本上哩類公厠狗 見到其他狗靜係識吠吠吠 一係就好驚 雖然佢地聰明但一d都唔忠心 唔會聽主人話 好有脾氣 其實係要用更多的耐性去教 令佢服從你 但我見好多哩種狗都做得麻麻地<br />\n睇你鍾意得意嘅狗定係型d嘅大狗 <br />\n細狗我就唔太清楚 但大狗一定係拉布拉多 夠friendly 又活潑 性格真係好 見好多狗友都係差不多 都忠心聽話聰明 如果唔係都唔搵哩款狗做導盲犬"},{"pid":"c1bce76e820359d6ca364f4bf02e2e971386a471","tid":87082,"uid":17799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T13:45:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咪聽上面話養貴婦